I"M<h1 id="zodiac">Zodiac</h1>
<p>In Zodiac, your task is to write a program that determines a person’s Chinese zodiac sign given their date of birth.
For example, if a person was born in 2008, his zodiac sign would be the <strong>rat</strong>.
A table of zodiac signs is below:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: center">Zodiac</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">Number</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">Rat (鼠)</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">1</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">Ox (牛)</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">2</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">Tiger (虎)</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">3</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">Rabbit (兔)</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">4</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">Dragon (龙)</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">5</td>
    </tr>
